court: IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY O. O. C. J. OFFICIAL LIQUIDATOR'S REPORT NO.70 OF 2007 IN COMPANY PETITION NO.59 OF 1984 In the matter of M/s. Fit Tight Nuts & Bolts Ltd. (in liqn.) .... Smt. R.R. Phanse. Mr. P. Ramarao, Official Liquidator present. ... CORAM: DR. D.Y. CHANDRACHUD, J. 21st June, 2007. P.C. : From the contents of paragraph 3 of the report it is evident that the workman has been paid the dues twice by inadvertence. In the circumstances, the report is made absolute in terms of prayer clause (a).
